request.description:
Crea un achievement.

Campos clave: title, description, quantity, goalAmount, targetType (enum), rewardAmount, rewardType (enum), image (media).

Ejemplo mínimo:
{
  "data": {
    "title": "Gana 10 partidas",
    "targetType": "gamesWon",
    "goalAmount": 10,
    "rewardType": "coins",
    "rewardAmount": 100
  }
}
